# Deployment scope — marketing site only (2026-05-31)
#
# The estimation tool is parked: its code stays in the repo, but its API
# functions are NOT deployed, to stay under Vercel's Hobby plan limit of 12
# Serverless Functions. Only the contact endpoint (and the email helper it
# imports) ship. To bring the tool back, delete the lines below and redeploy
# on a plan that allows enough functions.

# All estimator API functions (keep only contact.js)
api/*.js
!api/contact.js

# All estimator API libs (keep only email.js, which contact.js imports)
api/lib/*
!api/lib/email.js
